reviewText: THANK YOU, great service, DVD delivered in good quality! :)

We were sent a copy of the movie instead of the original, which we knew about ahead of time with the guarantee that it would be just as good as the original.  The sender said if we didn't like it he would refund our money.  I need to mention that we were also sent a copy of two other Philippino movies at no charge.  However, after several exchanges of e-mails and a few promises to fix the problem or refund the money, nothing has happened.
